I had another nightmare today.

1066
01:05:03,441 --> 01:05:05,026
One about Frank Hamer scolding me.

1067
01:05:07,028 --> 01:05:08,070
So, do you regret it?

1068
01:05:08,654 --> 01:05:11,574
