1113
01:07:53,527 --> 01:07:54,653
Platoon commander!

1114
01:07:55,988 --> 01:07:58,574
You need to come see this, sir.

1115
01:08:05,456 --> 01:08:07,124
Yes, this is Hoyang Police Station.

1116
01:08:08,959 --> 01:08:10,002
